What you need to know:  The 15,000 seater "Estadio Nacional de Cabo Verde", erected in 2010 and opened in 2014 has been the home base of the "Blue Sharks" as Cape Verde's national team is referred toFifa president Gianni Infantino on Monday urged member associations to rename a football facility in their respective countries after Pele who till date is the only player to have won three World Cups